hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Have you seen any good films recently? rdv-med.com NRA Chairman Shunichi Tanaka likened the stricken nuclearplant to a house of horrors at an amusement park. "I don't knowif describing it this way is appropriate, but it's like ahaunted house and, as I've said, mishaps keep happening oneafter the other," he told reporters. "We have to look into howwe can reduce the risks and how to prevent it from becoming afatal or serious incident."
